# Changelog

### Version 1.4.1
 - Bug fixed in the Enum field

### Version 1.4.0
 - Renamed module fields_ext to fields
 - Added Complexity validator
 - Added Password field
 - Updated Marshmallow to 2.1.0
 
### Version 1.3.3
 - Added forbidden method to the FlaskIO class.

### Version 1.3.2
 - Added member_type parameter to the Enum class to specify the type of the members.

### Version 1.3.1
 - Made Enum class compatible with marshmallow 2.0.0

### Version 1.3.0
 - Removed fields code and message from the error response.
 - Renamed field reason to code in the error response.

### Version 1.2.0
 - Just non http exceptions are logged.
 - Response with no payload the content_type will be text/html.

### Version 1.1.1
 - Added log on unhandled exceptions

### Version 1.1.0
 - Added Enum field which accept python Enum object.
 - Changed error message when the content-type is not supported.
